body.description: Straw Cover Cap for Stanley cup, 10mm Silicone Straw Topper Compatible with 30&40 Oz Tumbler with Handle, Dust-Proof Reusable Straw Tips Lids (Easter) Creative cartoon shape, cute and very decorative. The perfect gift for friends and family. Compatible with stanley tumbler 10mm straws. Please note that there are only silicone straw covers in your package, straws are not included.
